{
  "texts": [
    "As presented in Table 3, it is evident that MFCCs Feature Scaling-based representation produced the best audio-level accuracy, after which fusion with chromagram-based representation produced optimal features for the fusion.",
    "Multimodal fusion analysisIn this section, we analyze the impact of feature fusion.",
    "It was observed that fusing extracted features from audioimage and video provides better results than without fusion.",
    "However, empirically it has been shown that beyond simple concatenation, weights from one modality can influence fusion with the other modality.",
    "The best results are obtained when visual features and weights from the VMLP model interact with audio-image features."
  ]
}